---

<BaseLayout
  title="Crestmore Research — Premium Market Intelligence"
  description="Independent research and analysis across commodities, emerging markets, and global capital flows. Crestmore Research delivers institutional-grade intelligence for investment decision-makers."
  pageType="homepage"
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="hero hero--homepage" aria-label="Hero section">
    <div class="hero__bg-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero__bg-pattern"></div>
    <div class="container hero__container">
      <div class="hero__content">
        <p class="hero__eyebrow">Est. 2007 · New York · London · Singapore</p>
        <h1 class="hero__title">Independent Research<br /><em>That Moves Markets</em></h1>
        <p class="hero__subtitle">
          Crestmore Research delivers institutional-grade market intelligence across commodities, emerging markets, capital flows, and country risk. Our 200+ analyst team conducts primary research across 47 global markets, providing pension funds, sovereign wealth funds, and corporate strategy teams with evidence-backed analysis that transcends consensus. Founded on independence — no banking relationships, no conflicts, no compromises. Research for decision-makers who demand unbiased truth.
        </p>
        <div class="hero__actions">
          <a href="/research" class="btn btn--gold">Explore Research Library</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn--outline">Request a Brief</a>
          <a href="/sample-report" class="btn btn--outline-secondary">Download Sample Report</a>
        </div>
        <div class="hero__trust">
          <span>Trusted by 120+ institutional clients across 30+ countries</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Live market intelligence card -->
      <div class="hero__live-card">
        <div class="live-card">
          <div class="live-card__header">
            <span class="live-card__label">Live Market Intelligence</span>
            <span class="live-card__update">Updated 2 mins ago</span>
          </div>
          <div class="live-card__data">
            {liveData.map(item => (
              <div class="live-card__item">
                <span class="live-card__commodity">{item.commodity}</span>
                <span class="live-card__price">{item.price}</span>
                <span class={`live-card__change ${item.positive ? 'live-card__change--up' : 'live-card__change--down'}`}>
                  {item.change}
                </span>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="live-card__footer">
            <a href="/live-data" class="live-card__link">View full dashboard →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero__scroll-indicator" aria-hidden="true">
        <span></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       DATA TICKER
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="data-ticker" aria-label="Market intelligence ticker">
    <div class="ticker-content">
      {tickerHeadlines.map(headline => (
        <span class="ticker-item">{headline}</span>
      ))}
      {tickerHeadlines.map(headline => (
        <span class="ticker-item">{headline}</span>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       STATS BAR
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="stats-bar" aria-label="Key statistics">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="stats-bar__grid">
        {stats.map(stat => (
          <div class="stats-bar__item">
            <span class="stats-bar__value">{stat.value}</span>
            <span class="stats-bar__label">{stat.label}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       INTRODUCTION / POSITIONING (RICH)
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section section--intro" aria-labelledby="intro-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="intro__wrapper">
        <div class="intro__main">
          <p class="section__eyebrow">What Sets Us Apart</p>
          <h2 class="section__title" id="intro-title">Research Built for Decision-Makers, Not Desks</h2>

          <div class="intro__text-block">
            <p class="intro__para--lead">
              Crestmore Research was founded on a simple conviction: institutional investors deserve research that is genuinely independent — free from banking relationships, underwriting mandates, and sell-side conflicts of interest. That conviction drives everything we do.
            </p>

            <p class="intro__para">
              Over eighteen years, we have built one of the most respected independent research franchises in the market intelligence sector. Our analyst teams combine deep sector expertise with on-the-ground regional knowledge, delivering insights that move beyond consensus and challenge received wisdom. We conduct 200+ primary interviews annually with industry participants, government officials, and regional specialists. Our proprietary models are built in-house and stress-tested against decades of historical data.
            </p>

            <p class="intro__para">
              Our clients — pension funds, sovereign wealth funds, private equity firms, corporate treasury teams, and development finance institutions — rely on Crestmore for the full spectrum of research needs: from rapid situational briefs to multi-quarter engagement programmes. We serve 120+ institutional clients across 30+ countries.
            </p>

            <blockquote class="intro__pullquote">
              <span class="intro__quote-mark">"</span>
              <p>Independent research of genuine caliber is increasingly rare. What Crestmore has built — across commodities, country risk, and capital flows — sets a standard that few firms can match.</p>
              <span class="intro__quote-attrib">— Global Asset Allocator, $200B+ AUM</span>
            </blockquote>

            <a href="/about" class="intro__link">Learn more about Crestmore →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="intro__sidebar">
          <div class="intro__promise-box">
            <h3 class="intro__promise-title">Our Promise</h3>
            <ul class="intro__promise-list">
              <li><span class="promise-check">✓</span> Independence first, always</li>
              <li><span class="promise-check">✓</span> Primary research depth</li>
              <li><span class="promise-check">✓</span> Transparent methodology</li>
              <li><span class="promise-check">✓</span> Accountability & accuracy</li>
              <li><span class="promise-check">✓</span> Institutional-grade delivery</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="intro__image-container">
        <img src="/images/crestmore-research-team.jpg" alt="Crestmore Research analysts reviewing market intelligence" loading="lazy" class="intro__image" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       SECTOR EXPERTISE GRID
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section section--sectors section--bg-soft" aria-labelledby="sectors-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header section__header--center">
        <p class="section__eyebrow">Deep Expertise</p>
        <h2 class="section__title section__title--center" id="sectors-title">8 Sectors of Active Coverage</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Each sector represents 5+ years of dedicated analyst specialization and proprietary data development.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="sectors-grid">
        {sectors.map(sector => (
          <div class="sector-card">
            <h3 class="sector-card__title">{sector.title}</h3>
            <p class="sector-card__desc">{sector.desc}</p>
            <div class="sector-card__meta">
              <span class="sector-card__reports">{sector.reports} reports published</span>
            </div>
            <a href={`/sectors/${sector.id}`} class="sector-card__link">Explore sector →</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       FEATURED REPORTS SECTION
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section section--featured-reports" aria-labelledby="featured-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header section__header--center">
        <p class="section__eyebrow">From the Research Library</p>
        <h2 class="section__title section__title--center" id="featured-title">Flagship Reports</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Select recent publications from our institutional research program.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="featured-reports-grid">
        {featuredReports.map(report => (
          <div class="report-card">
            <div class="report-card__cover">
              <div class="report-card__category-tag">{report.category}</div>
              <div class="report-card__title">{report.title}</div>
              <div class="report-card__pages">{report.pages} pages</div>
            </div>
            <div class="report-card__footer">
              <a href={`/research/${report.slug}`} class="btn btn--small btn--gold">Download Sample</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
      <div class="section__cta-center">
        <a href="/research" class="btn btn--navy">Browse Full Research Library →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       SERVICES GRID
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section section--services" aria-labelledby="services-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header section__header--center">
        <p class="section__eyebrow">Our Capabilities</p>
        <h2 class="section__title section__title--center" id="services-title">Six Integrated Service Lines</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Comprehensive market intelligence covering the full research lifecycle — from primary data collection to institutional delivery.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        {services.map(svc => (
          <div class="service-card">
            <div class="service-card__icon" set:html={svc.icon} />
            <h3 class="service-card__title">{svc.title}</h3>
            <p class="service-card__desc">{svc.desc}</p>
            <a href="/services" class="service-card__link">Learn more →</a>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       CLIENT TYPES SECTION
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section section--client-types section--bg-soft" aria-labelledby="clients-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header section__header--center">
        <p class="section__eyebrow">Institutional Focus</p>
        <h2 class="section__title section__title--center" id="clients-title">Who We Work With</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Crestmore serves six primary institutional client categories, each with distinct intelligence requirements.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="client-types-grid">
        {clientTypes.map(client => (
          <div class="client-card">
            <h3 class="client-card__type">{client.type}</h3>
            <p class="client-card__desc">{client.desc}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       WHY CRESTMORE (Dark section)
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section section--dark section--why" aria-labelledby="why-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="why__grid">
        <div class="why__text">
          <p class="section__eyebrow section__eyebrow--gold">Our Principles</p>
          <h2 class="section__title section__title--light" id="why-title">The Crestmore Standard</h2>
          <div class="why__points">
            {whyPoints.map(point => (
              <div class="why__point">
                <div class="why__point-icon">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3>{point.title}</h3>
                  <p>{point.desc}</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why__visual">
          <img src="/images/crestmore-emerging-markets.jpg" alt="Emerging market coverage — Crestmore Research global presence" loading="lazy" class="why__image" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
       METHODOLOGY PREVIEW
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="section section--bg-soft" aria-labelledby="method-title">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section__header section__header--center">
        <p class="section__eyebrow">How We Work</p>
        <h2 class="section__title section__title--center" id="method-title">A Rigorous Four-Stage Process</h2>
        <p class="section__subtitle">Every Crestmore research deliverable passes through four structured stages — from primary data collection to peer-reviewed delivery.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="methodology-steps">
        {methodologySteps.map((step, i) => (
          <div class="method-step">
            <div class="method-step__num">{step.num}</div>
            <div class="method-step__content">
              <h3 class="method-step__title">{step.title}</h3>
              <p class="method-step__desc">{step.desc}</p>
            </div>
